commit d3a574f8d5b4333f63b5eb6712c28f4b49a8c013
Author: Bert Vermeulen <bert@biot.com>
Date:   Sun Feb 12 04:07:22 2012 +0100

    srd: extra module path can now optionally be passed to srd_init()
    
